nhdpIfStatus OBJECT-TYPE SYNTAX TruthValue MAX-ACCESS read-write STATUS current DESCRIPTION "The nhpdIfStatus indicates the current status of this NHDP device's interface with respect to supporting the NHDP protocol. A value of true(1) indicates that the interface is currently running the NHDP protocol. A value of false(2) indicates that the interface is currently not running the NHDP protocol." REFERENCE "RFC XXXX - ." DEFVAL { 2 } ::= { nhdpInterfaceEntry 2 }
